Crisis Resolution Rules May Be Needed for Insurers, EIOPA Says

-- B y   J i m   B r u n s d e n
-- 
2011-10-04T15:40:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/crisis-resolution-rules-may-be-needed-for-insurers-eiopa-says.html
Gabriel Bernardino, chairman of the
European Insurance and Occupational Pensions Authority, said the
need for crisis resolution rules for the insurance sector should
be considered. He made the comments at the European Parliament
today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
